metadata.name: Eye Congo Currency
metadata.description: eye congo currency is a collectors item that also teaches us about wealth, value, appreciation and how to have fun playing the money game. The coin is an actual physical copper coin of 40grams. upon purchase. the coin will be sent to you and the value in crypto added to your wallet. There is multi-value in this coin as it will give you access to exclusive IC deals and events, it  grow in value becasue it is tokenized with ethereum on the blockchain and it will grow in value because it is a limited edition copper collectable coin. thank you for your support and participation in this fun bountiful money game.
